# observe-logs environment registry.
# Copy this file to `.env` next to it, then `chmod 600 .env`.
# Format (pipe-delimited, one environment per line):
#   <env-name>|<grafana-proxy-url-with-uid>|<authorization-header-value>
# Lines starting with `#` and blank lines are ignored. This file is parsed, never sourced.
#
# stage|https://<grafana-host>/api/datasources/proxy/uid/<uid>|Bearer glsa_<token>
# dev|https://<grafana-host>/api/datasources/proxy/uid/<uid>|Bearer glsa_<token>
# prod|https://<grafana-host>/api/datasources/proxy/uid/<uid>|Bearer glsa_<token>
